id\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Los Angeles News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999996421138, \"rank\": 2.8315535315634053e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, last night, it was justspectacular,\\\" Biden said.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\", \"score\": 0.9999992581722859, \"rank\": 7.370325912834431e-07, \"text\": \"Biden\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The rain did not dampen our spirits.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step of the way, I was thinking to myself, 'Oh my god, oh my god.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How are we going to top this?'\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, ok. Paris has the Eiffel Tower, but we have Hollywood and the magic of Hollywood that makes all dreams come true.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999233751, \"rank\": 7.6708075686017e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999998038902, \"rank\": 